{"tid":1676622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG Misic Awards 2019 (連登討論區最愛女歌手五強提名post)","createTime":"2019-10-26T14:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T22:02:14.000Z","uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2cfe6168ccb5331c9c8ad211b229fb13217b9d36","tid":1676622,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【連登討論區最愛女歌手獎】</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLY9rJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLY9rJK.jpg&h=76ac7479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在post內提名，並且即時透過計算「正負皮淨值」選出金銀銅獎，提名需要是繁體中文全名或英文全名才有效，部份音樂人可能只有英文藝名，因此英文名亦可接受。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>提名：寫出歌手中文全名或英文名，如果有重複績計算第一個留言，計算正皮數值減負皮數值，以便得出最後五強</strong></span>，提名期至11月15日結束，多謝各位支持！"},{"pid":"376a79eabb15aa08fe261930796e3eb90e34156c","tid":1676622,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f38344c0dc2babc58d1cc2e3287fa575331594","tid":1676622,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"376a79eabb15aa08fe261930796e3eb90e34156c","tid":1676622,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"支持深紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b32f48577ae3a5fc23d43dfa8f385a774e39bd","tid":1676622,"uid":246787,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"泳兒"},{"pid":"e7648b5014de93998c677